data.name: tB_advises.Text
data.value:
Hello there, Here's some advise for use:
1: After you createded a saved projects, they'll be displayed In the right-top-corner, you can open them with double-click
2: You can add an image to your current-project by draggin it into this field, the image is then instantly redrawn, with the extracted contours
3: You have to save your project, before open another or closing the program or it will be lost!!!
4: In the ContourList, you may select and delete Contours, Highlighted in the Picture. (You can go throug them with up- and down Arrows and delete them fast with the Deletekey)
5: You can use this Progam without Mouse or Touchpad, just use 'Tab' to switch to the next textfield or Button (or 'ctrl + tab' to switch in the other direction), 'Enter' to activate Buttons and 'up-/downArrorws' to navigate in Lists
6: The Picture is displayed in the best way, if the Materialproperties are those of your Picture, but for your GCode you have to use the correct materialproperties for obviously reasons
